reviews.review_text: My boyfriend and I came here for dinner, we shared an avocado salad, I got the vegetarian pho and he got a beef teriyaki. Food was yummy, Ive not had pho for a while and I really enjoyed it. The avocado salad was also good. The atmosphere was interesting similar to maybe a sports bar. Lots of great food options and good service. We will be back for sure.

Everything was great from the food to the service we received. The staff is friendly and are well versed on their menu. We ordered the Jappa Fries which were so good. We also had the Beef don and it was also really good the sauce just makes it 10x better. The vibes are great when going out with friends before going out for the night.
Great service, not too busy on a Wednesday but not empty either. The portions were good for the price and the flavors are also good. Would come back to try Happy Hour with friends for sure

So much fun here! Great for birthdays or simply dinner and drinks with friends. The layout of the restaurant makes it easy for dining guests to interact with each other. Highly recommended bar to check out if youre looking for good food and fun.

I really enjoy the food at this place.  The chef is a master of sauces!  Literally went to three restaurants this week this was by far the best meal!!! Servers are very friendly and give friendly service.  Love the atmosphere. Yeeun was lovely to have as a server.  Excellent service.

I came here the first time back in 2017, this time I was in the area and so happy to see its still in business today. Stopped by here for happy hour and really enjoyed everything from the food, drinks, and the service. I love asian bar foods, definitely recommend and will come back for more happy hour!

Food was amazing . Tried  new things and loved it . Sushi pizza???  Hell ya  loved it ... fried salmon belly hell yessssssss.    Japa balls ....Sooooo good.  I will be back to try the rest .  Loved it . Thank you

Lovely Asian bar. The food was really fresh, big size, beautifully presented and delicious. Their avocado salad was so good and filling. The atmosphere felt comfortable enough to enjoy the surroundings and enjoy who I was with. Food was delivered in a prompt manner and the servers were friendly.

Was recommended the Beef Don by the staff. Impossibly delicious. Had California rolls, also impossibly delicious. Saporro on tap? You can see where Im going with this. Music was the perfect volumeand the place was comfortably busy but not jammed. Simply an impossibly delicious visit, would recommend to everyone. Thanks to the staff, you knocked it out of the park!! Vegetarian options: Saw veggie items on the menu Kid-friendliness: Sushi for kids!
Amazing Happy Hour! Cheap drinks and good food! Service was impeccable!

Simply Delicious Restaurant & Bar is an absolute gem that left me glowing with joy after my visit. The moment I stepped inside, I was transported to a world that reminded me of the vibrant atmosphere depicted in the movie Coyote Ugly. The energetic ambiance and the presence of the attentive and empathetic servers truly made me feel like I was among Simply Delicious Angels, who could effortlessly grace the cover of any fashion magazine. From the very beginning, my experience at Simply Delicious exceeded my expectations. I decided to start with their oysters, and oh boy, they were a true delight! Fresh, succulent, and bursting with flavor, each bite was a reminder of the exceptional quality of their seafood. Accompanying the oysters was a generous portion of edamame, which was not only delicious but also served in a quantity that left me feeling satisfied. As a fan of classic cocktails, I couldnt resist ordering an Old Fashioned. To my surprise, despite the bartenders mentioning it was their first time making it, the drink was nothing short of perfection. The balance of flavors, the careful attention to detail, and the impeccable execution were indicative of the exceptional skill and talent present in the bar staff. However, it was not just the outstanding food and drinks that impressed me at Simply Delicious; it was the extraordinary service that truly stole the show. When I arrived, I was feeling down after a challenging day, having lost my job. Yet, the staff, especially two individuals named Yeeun and Julie, went above and beyond to make me feel welcome and cared for. Their warmth, friendliness, and genuine empathy turned my mood around completely. By the end of my visit to Simply Delicious, I left with a renewed sense of happiness. What started as a simple need for a drink turned into an experience that exceeded all my expectations. The exceptional quality of the food, the flawless execution of the drinks, and the remarkable service from the staff created a perfect storm of satisfaction and contentment. If youre looking for a place to lift your spirits and indulge in culinary delights, Simply Delicious Restaurant & Bar is the place to be. Its a haven where the food is exceptional, the service is extraordinary, and the atmosphere transports you to a world of joy. Trust me when I say that a visit to Simply Delicious will leave you with a smile on your face and a heart full of happiness.

The best spot Ive found in quite a while. Its above other business and has a crazy intimate atmosphere. It has happy hour late into the night with great food and drinks going on discount. We ordered lots of plates and got to share everything. Was really good value and quality food. Service was also amazing. Would be a great place go to with friends after a night out.
Surprise birthday party, great food, drinks and atmosphere! Service was top notch! Would definitely go again!! Vegetarian options: Vegetarian Bahn mi was extremely good!
Best prices in town. Easily can accommodate large groups, would love to go back for the happy hour!
Love this place! They are open super late, they have a huge menu, and the drinks are fire! Ask for an extra dirty gin martini
Great atmosphere and friendly staff. Owner offer free shooters to us. I will definitely go back for karage wings and beans

Ive been coming here for a long time and have always received great service and fresh food. During COVID, theyve outdone themselves! Their takeout containers are sturdy, reusable, recyclable or compostable. Their to-go bag is paper too! They even use cucumber slices instead of those fake plastic grass strips to separate the wasabi and ginger from the food. Even though theyve doubled their prices, (an expensive $6/roll), I was happy to support this place during these crazy times. Lower your prices a bit please

We were looking for a late night bowl of Pho and this place delivered. I am picky about my pho broth and this was really good. Not just salty water but spiced like traditional pho. The waitress was very nice and we all left happy. If you need a late night bite, this place has what you want.

We ordered five dishes and four out of five were amazing, the fifth was good but not as good as other places. Happy Hour specials were great, and the atmosphere was awesome! Will definitely go back if given the opportunity!

Great place and a bit of a hidden gem! Ive been out on main many times and this was my first time there. The food came out fast and it was really good. Service was excellent as well... thank you for taking care of our large party. You guys rock!!! ~The Moose
They  added a Vietnamese menu and its delicious. Soups and Sandwiches are my favorite. As always good drink specials
The food is delicious also the staffs were so friendly

Food and drink selection + quality is great! Wonderful place to be solo or with friends as the restaurant has a nice vibrant atmosphere, especially during sporting events. The outdoor patio is also very nice and a great place to chill & dine away from the busy polluting traffic below, as its high up on the 2nd floor with lots of beautiful vegetation that helps separate you from the outside reality, for the most part. Staff are totally awesome & are very attentive to your dining needs. Two thumbs up, way up, for overall dining experience!!! Love it here!
Fun atmosphere and good food. Dine in is great and opening hours are convenient
Had my post wedding party and my post marriage certificate signing party here. Best bar ever. Love you Sylvia <3
Amazing sushi, friendly staff, reasonable prices

I havent been here for a while.  I was grateful to my friend  who brought me back to this restaurant last night, and my experience was extremely satisfying with friendly service and quality food.  I will definitely be back more often and let all my friends know about this place.
Food was very creative; you need to try the sushi pizza! Serving staff was great, accommodating a full jazz band.

The sushi was immaculate and the service was amazing. I really liked the spicy tuna and the dynamite rolls. The sake bomb was so fun and it tasted great! I would reccomend this place for any type of event, if youre going for a birthday or even just a dinner with friends or even a date! Its great for all.
Very fun environment. Generous food portions. Will be back again.
Consistently great food! We ve ordered here multiple times for the last couple of years and have never been disappointed. They definitely live up to their name  Simply Delicious
Great little spot-  had a couple amazing appies & 2 cold sappora Beers.  Pleasant and happy place to Enjoy time with friends. Food : 5/5

Not sure where else i can find late night happy hour oysters but for now, this is my go to spot. $2 oysters and theyve been miyagis so far which is awesome. Definitely recommend if youre an oyster fan

Such an amazing place to chill whether its with a group of friends or if its just a date. The sushi here is the best i have had so far. The drinks are amazing as well. The staff is so friendly you would not feel like its your first time there. They treat you so nicely and respectfully. The manager Silvia is such a beautiful person inside and out. She makes an effort to meet all her customers when she is there. I met her on our first visit to the place and she has been a delight everytime we have been there. Her team is as fantastic as she is. Even on a busy game day like today,i noticed she made an effor to go to each table and speak to her guests. She is amazing,her team is amazing, this place is fantastic. If you are in Vancouver, you MUST visit here!! Thank you Simply Delicious team and Silvia for making my every visit more special than the last.

Great atmosphere and service, always such a graceful hosts. Really enjoy their menu and of course their daily specials. I recommend their veganlicious roll, beef yaki udon and signature japa fries and the many more items in the menu! Theres something for everyone. Simplys is a place where I can go after work and do not feel the rush to leave. Every so often they come up with new cocktails and shots they are dangerously refreshing and leaves you wanting more.

I have yet to order something short of fabulous on the menu here, I taste the love in the food everytime   As well a great atmosphere and always such warm welcoming staff, especially the owners! The Shaft cocktail is a must try for coffee lovers

This place is kind of bonkers. Like its set up as a karaoke place but also has a very thorough menu with almost anything you can dream of. The staff is very friendly and the food is actually decent for having 1000 options. Would go again.
One of my favourite stops!!! Love it here, would completely recommend!!<3

This is my go-to Sushi restaurant whenever I order takeout. Their presentation is beautiful, well-handled and thought out. Whoever added a heart and a smiley face on the takeout bag is an awesome person and I always felt as if I was dining in with them. Their portions is balanced and worth every bite. I ordered almost everything on the menu and my favorite is the chicken fried rice because its taste brought back fond memories of my travels in Asia, its that good. I hope they add more selections of Nigiri combos in the future, thatd be cool. Give Simply Delicious a try, its simply delicious!

My son & daughter in law took me here for dinner. The service was amazing, great drinks menu, food is fantabulous. What a tasty variety of foods. Most definately recommwnd checking this awesome place out. Staff are very quick & friendly too
$4 Happy hour beers aint bad. In fact happy hour altogether is great here, would recommend

Open late night - I ve only ordered take out, but its really good! Big fan!! Ordered the karaage wings my first order and had to get delivery a second time the same week cus I be craving those wings haha love the veganlicious roll too, although it is priced the same as other house rolls that have fish, unagi so it s hard to order.
Delicious food at an amazing price. Happy hour menu is the way to go. Waitress was very attentive too!
I ve not had the opportunity to go to the restaurant, but yes to try their delicious food through DoorDash. My favourite the spicy Combo. They also write a sweet message with the delivery.

Ordered on Uber Eats, very fast and accurate food preparation estimate, food arrived nice and hot. Got an order of Karaage wings with chilli lime pepper sauce, these were hot, crispy and delicious with lots of wings. Flavour on the wings was slightly lacking (maybe forgot a bit of seasoning in the batter?) But when dunked in the sauce these were insanely delicious!! Will be ordering again just for them! Also got a salmon sushi roll which was great too! Although I would love if they had a salmon avocado roll on the menu!

Amazing and fresh Japanese fusion food. The Japafries is a must order, the dipping sauce is to die for. We went there for happy hour and got fresh oysters and cheap and delicious appetizers. Worth every penny. The wings were crispy and comes in many Asian fusion flavors. Appies were 4$ wings were 8$ highballs 4$. A hidden gem on main st
Visited during happy hour, nice food with good value. Server was really nice and gave good recommendation
Great service,staff was extremely nice. Rare these days... Food was awesome. They have a sushi pizza that is killer
I love this place. The foods great, its huge so theres always seating even for big groups. Plus it somehow manages to feel relaxed and laid back while still being attentive.

I order delivery from them all the time, order is perfect and a good temperature every time. Packed great with a nice note, and they cater to my adjustments wonderfully. Thank you guys, love what youre doing.

One of the hidden gems of Vancouver. The whole squid is lovely, and check out their dessert menu for deep fried bananas and Mars bars! In the summer, sit on their balcony overlooking Main St., And people watch to your hearts content. Just dont get the bowl, or more than a dozen oysters

Got Uber Eats and it arrived fresh and tasted great :) Best value for taste, size and freshness ! Staff are also awesome as they gave me extra carrot dressing at no charge  :) They earned a new customer.
Best food you can imagine for the price. And the happy hour oxtail pho is better than anything else Ive had in Canada
Little gem. Staff are great, food is really great. Unique spot that is fun with a group. Patio is a hidden gem. Its a little weird but in a good way. Try the oysters.
Shout out to Emma, for the awesome servicE. Would recommend this place. Pretty chill, she got us lit lol  .
Well food was delicious and drinks were cheap and make sure to as for a supper nice waiters MS AN. Saturday and Sundays cheers.
I Absolutely love this place! It always has seats never any lineups to get in. Food is awesome and the drinks are cheap. By far my favorite place on Main street.
Relaxed  beautiful  setting But best chicken and a great house dressing   Prices are  not high.  But the service is high class... Great choice of non alcoholic beverages
20 years and still simply delicious!!

Place is the DEFINITION of RANDOM.. in a gooood way! Feels like a college karaoke sports bar (with korean fusion). Cheap drinks, decently priced asian inspired pub food, large seating areas, massive projectors for sports. PLEASE dont expect fine-dining. Its cheap and full of randomness for a reason. Ill definitely back.
Great atmosphere, very friendly and attentive staff. Delicious food and great drink specials. Good place to get together with friends and have a good time.
We were very happy  during the happy hour. Good food & liquor. Excellent service of waiter & waitresses.
Ive been going to this sushi bar for 5 years now and I love it. The staff is great and the food is amazing!! The owner nam and his wife are really great comforting people.
Simply Delicious   awesome place, with great vibes. Open late so great for all time munchies.
Great service and the Happy Hour is on point!
Ordered for takeout. Food was fast and fresh with a nice message on the bag. Can t wait to try dining in when things open up again.
Food is amazing, atmosphere is great. If I lived close by Id be there weekly!
Love the atmosphere and the food is excellent. Thumb up for An for the best friendly service.
Been going for 10+ years! Great bar & grill type of atmosphere that you dont find at most sushi places

Now I know why they call it simply D..... Cause it was delicious... SIMPLE... THERE FOOD WAS AWESOME... the service from the lovely ladies was nothing to complain about.... And there drink specials..... You cant beat.... Any where.... Simple
Great place to either catch the game or just chill and talk with friends. Management and staff always make you feel at home. Awesome atmosphere.
Very chill bar, unfortunately visited during the day, but feels like a lit place at night
Love this place, go here often. Good food for descent price . Easy to try lots of small dishes and they are all good
Always great food. Servers are always rotating and doesnt seem to be consistent. Great for late night eats and cravings
Amazing as always! The food never disappoints, the staff and owners are always so welcoming and the atmosphere is always a good vibe!
Omg. Fresh.  Best roll ive ever had. I am ompreased so far.  Thank you. My new favorite place.
Amazing food & really good service! The entertainment was beyond amazing! 19 piece jazz band. Best night ever!
Great atmosphere. A little on the pricey side but good food and even better service!
Great spot on second floor with varied menu and great service. Always a fun time hanging out with some shots!
Great prices, staff and atmosphere! We got food and a couple of beers. Not disappointed.
Great place for large parties or small. Tons of room. Great staff. And they always have specials !
Good food, good prices, good vibes. Go on a Tuesday or Sunday night for a fun time, the karaoke host is a blast!
Awesome price for happy hour and late night snack ! Food is fresh !
Waitresses are very nice and also very attractive:) first time coming yesterday loved there vibe
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hello Matt <3 Thank your for your wonderful review and your continuous support :)

reviews.review_text: Great staff, great owners, great food and drinks, and great service. Ask for the nimal wings if u like spicy wings
Very good. If you like japanese food with some extra flavour, this is the place for you.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you Nuilo22 . We are happy to hear you had a great experience :)

reviews.review_text: very chic place with yummy appy plates that shareable !
Some of the tastiest sushi I ve had in Vancouver. The fried chicken is on point too
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you Alex for your review <3 We really appreciate the support :)

reviews.review_text: Still great, even though covid makes things difficult. Good food, excellent service; chill place to visit
Late night sushi with decent quality and decent prices. What more can I say, its easy to love
Great spot for some late night drinks and small plates. Always a good atmosphere!
Fun place, great casual fusion. Good drink specials!
Its a nice and chill restaurant. I love the salmon don
Excellent friendly service and so happy to find great food open late.
Been here many times over the years as their menu went to being Vietnamese/Japanese to just Japanese. Still as good as always.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you very much for the 5 star Review. We really appreciate it :)

reviews.review_text: The service is always amazing and the food and beer is always fresh and delicious :)
Great happy hour deals, cool staff, friendly atmosphere.
Great Food,  atmosphere and service.   Will definitely be going back.
Great spot to chill even on a Monday, Yeeun is very friendly and accommodating
The prices here great, servers are wonderful and theres always somewhere to sit.
